Comments:       ----------
                Setup and usage in 3 easy steps:

                1. $ mkdir -p $HOME/.config/minidlna

                2. Create $HOME/.config/minidlna/minidlna.conf, like this example:
                media_dir=/mnt/usb/Media
                friendly_name=My DLNA Server

                3. $ minidlnad -f $HOME/.config/minidlna/minidlna.conf
